[normal]4e. 
[normal]Women’s Group
[normal]Women on both sides of the conflict need to be empowered to realize their own strengths and unique abili
[normal]ty to conduct a dialogue and to acknowledge the role of women in the path to reconciliation.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]UN resolution 1325 affirms the important role of women in the prevention and resolution of conflicts, peace negotiations, peace-building, peacekeeping
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]and 
[normal]humanita
[normal]rian response.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] With all of this in mind
[normal],
[normal] the PCFF
[normal] h
[normal]as created a powerful group of bereaved women who are fast becoming important players in the maintenance and promotion of peace and security.
